Class CommandClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.MudPitBot.botCommand.CommandClient

  • public class CommandClient
extends java.lang.Object
    A client class for the Command design pattern. A client is an object that controls the command execution process by specifying what commands to execute and at what stages of the process to execute them. https://www.baeldung.com/java-command-pattern
